{"text_id":8479,"tokens":["The"," question"," regarding"," the"," leave"," policies"," for"," Roman"," legion","aries"," and"," the"," consequences"," for"," those"," who"," deserted"," during"," their"," leave"," is"," a"," complex"," one",","," as"," it"," pertains"," to"," various"," factors"," such"," as"," the"," historical"," period",","," the"," specific"," legion",","," and"," the"," individual"," circumstances"," of"," each"," soldier","."," However",","," general"," trends"," can"," be"," identified",".","\n\n","Roman"," legion","aries"," were"," indeed"," granted"," leave",","," known"," as"," '","comme","atus","',"," throughout"," their"," ","2","5","-","year"," service"," period","."," The"," frequency"," of"," these"," leaves"," and"," their"," duration"," depended"," on"," a"," variety"," of"," factors",","," including"," the"," legion","'","s"," current"," military"," operations",","," the"," soldier","'","s"," rank",","," and"," his"," personal"," circumstances","."," It"," is"," estimated"," that"," a"," legion","ary"," might"," receive"," a"," '","comme","atus","'"," every"," few"," years",","," although"," the"," exact"," interval"," is"," not"," clear"," due"," to"," the"," disparity"," in"," our"," sources",".","\n\n","The"," Roman"," military"," was"," cogniz","ant"," of"," the"," importance"," of"," maintaining"," a"," strong"," bond"," between"," its"," soldiers"," and"," their"," families","."," Therefore",","," leave"," was"," generally"," granted"," for"," important"," personal"," reasons",","," such"," as"," attending"," a"," family"," funeral"," or"," marrying","."," However",","," leave"," was"," not"," an"," automatic"," right",","," and"," it"," had"," to"," be"," requested"," and"," approved",".","\n\n","As"," for"," those"," who"," deserted"," while"," on"," leave",","," the"," Roman"," state"," took"," a"," stern"," approach","."," Des","ertion"," was"," considered"," a"," serious"," offense",","," punishable"," by"," death",".","